import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown, Container, Form, FormControl, button } from "react-bootstrap"
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import { GoalTips } from "../ApiManager"

const [suggestions, setSuggestions] = useState([])

useEffect(() => {
    GoalTips()
    .then((data) => {
        setSuggestions(data)
    })
},[])


export const NavigationBar = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
        <Container>
          <Navbar.Brand href="/home">Goalify</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
          <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
            <Nav className="me-auto">
              <Nav.Link href="/goalform">Create A Goal</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link href="/mygoals">My Goals</Nav.Link>
              <NavDropdown title="Goalsetting Tips" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">

                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">
                  Action
                </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">
                  Another action
                </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">
                  Something
                </NavDropdown.Item>
                <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">
                  Separated link
                </NavDropdown.Item>
              </NavDropdown>
            </Nav>
            <Nav>
              <Nav.Link href="#deets">More deets</Nav.Link>
              <Nav.Link eventKey={2} href="/login">
                Logout
              </Nav.Link>
            </Nav>
          </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
      </Navbar>
    </>
  );
};
